#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an8.16"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.16:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Mahāvagga "
msgstr "2. The Great Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Dūteyyasutta "
msgstr "16. Going on a Mission "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.196, sc1
msgctxt "an8.16:1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu dūteyyaṃ gantumarahati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a mendicant with eight qualities is worthy of going on a mission. "

msgctxt "an8.16:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "an8.16:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sotā ca hoti, sāvetā ca, uggahetā ca, dhāretā ca, viññātā ca, viññāpetā ca, kusalo ca sahitāsahitassa, no ca kalahakārako—"
msgstr "It’s a mendicant who learns and educates others. They memorize and help others remember. They understand and help others understand. They’re skilled at knowing what’s on topic and what isn’t. And they don’t cause quarrels. "

msgctxt "an8.16:1.4"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu dūteyyaṃ gantumarahati. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these eight qualities is worthy of going on a mission. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.16:1.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato sāriputto dūteyyaṃ gantumarahati. "
msgstr "Having eight qualities Sāriputta is worthy of going on a mission. "

msgctxt "an8.16:1.6"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "an8.16:1.7"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, sāriputto sotā ca hoti, sāvetā ca, uggahetā ca, dhāretā ca, viññātā ca, viññāpetā ca, kusalo ca sahitāsahitassa, no ca kalahakārako. "
msgstr "He learns and educates others. He memorizes and helps others remember. He understands and helps others understand. He’s skilled at knowing what’s on topic and what isn’t. And he doesn’t cause quarrels. "

msgctxt "an8.16:1.8"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahi dhammehi samannāgato sāriputto dūteyyaṃ gantumarahatīti. "
msgstr "Having these eight qualities Sāriputta is worthy of going on a mission. "

# NOTE: Reading navedhati
#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
#. VAR: na byathati → navedhati (bj) | na byādhati (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an8.16:2.1"
msgid "Yo ve na byathati patvā, "
msgstr "They don’t tremble when arriving "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: uggavādiniṃ → uggavādinaṃ (si) | uggahavādinaṃ (s1-3, pts1) | uggatavādiniṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an8.16:2.2"
msgid "parisaṃ uggavādiniṃ; "
msgstr "at an assembly of fierce debaters. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.16:2.3"
msgid "Na ca hāpeti vacanaṃ, "
msgstr "They don’t omit any words, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.16:2.4"
msgid "na ca chādeti sāsanaṃ. "
msgstr "or conceal the instructions. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an8.16:3.1"
msgid "Asandiddhañca bhaṇati, "
msgstr "Their words aren’t poisoned, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.16:3.2"
msgid "Pucchito na ca kuppati; "
msgstr "and they don’t tremble when questioned. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.16:3.3"
msgid "Sa ve tādisako bhikkhu, "
msgstr "Such a mendicant "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.16:3.4"
msgid "Dūteyyaṃ gantumarahatī”ti. "
msgstr "is worthy of going on a mission.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.16:3.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
